      "methodClassification": "estimated with assumptions",
      "methodClassificationDescription": "The total DMI for the farm is 117.9 tonnes. The average percentage of DMI coming from external feed is 3% (this was calculated as a weighted average across all farms from Table 8 in the study). This leaevs 97% DMI coming from forage. So the value here was calculated as Total DMI * 97%.",
      "properties": [
